OL,3,CPensions 'could be used to help
OL,4,Cworkers build a rainy day savings pot'
OL,6,FThe next decade of workplace pensions
OL,7,Fsaving should be more flexible and
OL,8,Fhelp low earners to build up a savings
OL,9,Fsafety net that they can draw on
OL,10,Fbefore they retire, according to a
OL,11,Fthink tank.
OL,13,FThe Resolution Foundation said more
OL,14,Ffocus is needed on addressing the
OL,15,Fdifferent challenges faced by low,
OL,16,Fmiddle and higher earners.
OL,18,FIt said the first decade of automatic
OL,19,Fenrolment into workplace pensions has
OL,20,Fimproved private pension coverage and
OL,21,Fboosted people's savings pots.
