OL,3,CPensions 'could be used to help
OL,4,Cworkers build a rainy day savings pot'
OL,6,FBut while a "one-size-fits-all"
OL,7,Fapproach has worked well for the first
OL,8,Fchapter of auto-enrolment, the next
OL,9,Fchapter will require both a boost to
OL,10,Fsaving rates and a more flexible
OL,11,Fapproach, to reflect the different
OL,12,Fchallenges that low, middle and higher
OL,13,Fearners face, it added.
OL,15,FThe report argues that default
OL,16,Fcontribution rates into auto-enrolment
OL,17,Fshould continue to rise over the next
OL,18,Fdecade, initially from 8% to 10%.
