OL,3,CPensions 'could be used to help
OL,4,Cworkers build a rainy day savings pot'
OL,6,FBut it said the additional funds from
OL,7,Fthis next phase of rising contribution
OL,8,Frates should go into an easy-access
OL,9,F"sidecar" savings account, with any
OL,10,Fbalance more than #1,000 then flowing
OL,11,Finto an employee's pension.
OL,13,FIts report said: "It is time to view
OL,14,Fpensions as part of a broader savings
OL,15,Fstrategy designed to balance the twin
OL,16,Fobjectives of retirement and
OL,17,Fprecautionary saving rather than
OL,18,Fpitting them against one another."
