OL,3,CPensions 'could be used to help
OL,4,Cworkers build a rainy day savings pot'
OL,6,FOne in three working-age adults live
OL,7,Fin families with accessible savings of
OL,8,Fless than #1,000, the foundation,
OL,9,Fwhich is focused on improving the
OL,10,Fliving standards of those on low-to-
OL,11,Fmiddle incomes, said.
OL,13,FThe proposed saving boost and added
OL,14,Fflexibility would help low earners
OL,15,Fbalance building up their rainy day
OL,16,Fsavings while maintaining their
OL,17,Fcurrent rate of pension saving ` and
OL,18,Falso help higher earners, who are more
OL,19,Flikely to already have savings, to
OL,20,Ffurther boost their pension pots, the
OL,21,Freport argued.
