OL,3,CPensions 'could be used to help
OL,4,Cworkers build a rainy day savings pot'
OL,6,FMolly Broome, an economist at the
OL,7,FResolution Foundation, said: "Twenty
OL,8,Fyears ago, and amid widespread
OL,9,Fconcerns about poverty in later life,
OL,10,Fthe Pensions Commission set benchmarks
OL,11,Ffor how much people would need to save
OL,12,Fduring their working lives to enjoy a
OL,13,Fdecent income in retirement.
OL,15,F"Policies like the new state pension
OL,16,Fand auto-enrolment have delivered on
OL,17,Ftheir objective of giving everyone a
OL,18,Fdecent minimum level of retirement
OL,19,Fincome. But the job is incomplete.
