OL,3,CPensions 'could be used to help
OL,4,Cworkers build a rainy day savings pot'
OL,6,F"And so the new Government's Pensions
OL,7,FReview, which could set policy for the
OL,8,Fnext decade, should focus on tackling
OL,9,Fthe different savings challenges that
OL,10,Flow, middle and higher earners face.
OL,12,F"As well as continuing to boost
OL,13,Fpension saving, auto-enrolment also
OL,14,Fneeds to be more flexible. It should
OL,15,Fallow low earners to build up rainy
OL,16,Fday savings that they can draw on
OL,17,Fbefore retirement, while higher
OL,18,Fcontributions for higher earners could
OL,19,Fhelp them get closer to maintaining
OL,20,Ftheir level of living standards into
OL,21,Fretirement."
