OL,6,FThe report was funded by People's
OL,7,FPartnership, provider of the People's
OL,8,FPension.
OL,10,FPatrick Heath-Lay, chief executive of
OL,11,FPeople's Partnership, said: "For
OL,12,Fmillions, the combination of legal
OL,13,Fminimum pension contributions and the
OL,14,Fstate pension will totally determine
OL,15,Ftheir quality of life in retirement.
OL,16,FAny conversation about the future of
OL,17,Fpensions saving needs to start with
OL,18,Fthe question 'how much is enough?'."
